title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Your impressive ability to launch deep and hard into whatever needs to be done is both feared and respected by those around you. You might shield your time and resources so you can concentrate on your mission without compromise or distraction today. However, your singular focus can give you tunnel-vision and even a certain intolerance for those who arent fully on board with the task at hand. Dont be dismissive of people who are plugged into different priorities. You may regret brushing off folks who need your immediate emotional support. Balance is essential if you hope to sleep well at night. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
